subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] Re: Letter connections and syllable boundaries (or, the spelling of "kangaroo")
msgSnippet: I would like to see some sort of consistent list of QS letter names, Lexical Set names, etc. that have been tossed around lately. I m not smart enough to dig
messageBody:
I would like to see some sort of consistent list of
QS letter names, Lexical Set names, etc. that have
been tossed around lately.

I'm not smart enough to dig through the previous
emails to extract the information, some messages are
just plain confusing. Lists might help.

--- Moira O'Brien <mj@...> wrote:
> I find I am getting very confused with the names for
> the letters which
> you are all using. I know the QM names,
> and I have all John Zuk's names (which I like) but I
> dont understand
> these new names you all seem to be using.
> Where to they come from?

===========
Never insult anyone by accident.
- Robert A. Heinlein
